{"tid":2478564,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"調較汽車響咹大細聲","createTime":"2021-04-07T07:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T07:20:18.000Z","uid":57307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a9342f3f403bdf70bf1935b80dfbfaab72ee3549","tid":2478564,"uid":57307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"有冇得調較?<br />\n<br />\n我屋苑出入一定要更亭食蕉開閘<br />\n有時佢冇留意我架車嚟到，我個響咹都幾大聲，次次大聲響咹提佢好似唔太友善，有次深夜出去，閃咗幾十下高燈都唔知我嚟到，9下9下只顧做自己嘢<br />\n<br />\n有時留意到有啲van響咹可以細細聲, 有冇ching知點解有呢隻courtesy horn？"},{"pid":"614d568e7f14acce06025fb64a3a511033ea2d84","tid":2478564,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:03:51.000Z","msg":"細力d拍2下咪算"},{"pid":"adecb81de228acd2a536fbe8c4d643a2ea795fe8","tid":2478564,"uid":296589,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS8YQKPNLXPm3aYrnPy4m1UWQr4YNNXr63JTTZxjV6iR9?filename=yU2BYq0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyU2BYq0.jpg&h=54005d63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"984f9317644ac17089e7f221cd5d0685f5bd5e7f","tid":2478564,"uid":217641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:10:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.servicebellapp&amp;hl=en&amp;gl=US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.servicebellapp%26hl%3Den%26gl%3DUS&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtN%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=f98db5bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.servicebellapp&amp;hl=en&amp;gl=US</a>"},{"pid":"b8a141364456c9c52eda22c43b4f8a388f27bcc8","tid":2478564,"uid":13084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:10:44.000Z","msg":"用風按"},{"pid":"f61f8fa155d1c27ca1393d90043fa58736e70e5d","tid":2478564,"uid":217641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07